  "definition": {
    "en": "Telmisartan, when dried, contains not less than 99."
  },
  "appearance": {
    "en": "Telmisartan occurs as a white to pale yellow crystalline powder. Time after injection of sample (min) Mobile phase A (volz) Mobile phase B (volz) It is freely soluble in formic acid, slightly soluble in metha-nol, very slightly soluble in ethanol (99.5), and practically in-soluble in water. It shows crystal polymorphism."
